sequenceDiagram
    participant GameController
    participant Player
    participant Maze
    GameController->>GameController: Initialize
    GameController->>Maze: Create Maze
    Maze-->>GameController: Maze Instance
    GameController->>Player: Create Player
    Player-->>GameController: Player Instance
    GameController->>Maze: SetPlayerStart()
    Maze->>Player: SetPosition(startPosition)
    Player-->>Maze: Position Updated
    GameController->>Player: Initialize Controls
    Player-->>GameController: Ready
    GameController->>Maze: GetMazeLayout()
    Maze-->>GameController: Layout Data
    GameController-->>GameController: Game Ready